description: Aybla Mediterranean Grill is very proud of every item we serve made with creativity, flavor and warm hospitality.Much of our produce is organic from our local Farmer’s Market. We use fresh feta, olives and bread that are authentically Mediterranean.Please feel free to ask the Chef, Saied, for any special requests. We are here to serve you from our five Portland locations. We want to you feel as welcome as you would in your own home.We are also happy to offer catering for your special events, weddings, office meetings, etc. We provide delivery along with great prices. Choose from our standard menu items such as our amazing gyros, vegetarian dishes, unique appetizers and delicious kabobs.Thanks very much for coming by!Chef Saied
name: Aybla Grill
